thread.title: Oil Prices Rise, Building on Gains After Drop in Crude Stockpiles

author: Alison Sider
title: Oil Prices Rise, Building on Gains After Drop in Crude Stockpiles
text:
A surprise drop in U.S. crude stockpiles and halted production at a Libyan oil field helped lift oil prices Friday, extending their rally to a second week.
Oil prices have climbed more than 7% in the last two weeksâ€”the biggest two-week gain since November.
